  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/89ea7d692a7c1365fea9670d13eb3d44.avif?t=1748595734\" width=600 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/eb5cf0e104843acee9bb55439bea7bda.poster.avif?t=1748595734\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/eb5cf0e104843acee9bb55439bea7bda.webm?t=1748595734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/eb5cf0e104843acee9bb55439bea7bda.mp4?t=1748595734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Victory or defeat depends on the placement of your cards, timing of usage, and combinations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own tactics and unleash unpredictable plays!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/b45043d54d9a914f301cfd27b0e8c3d0.avif?t=1748595734\" width=600 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/6b246f27b7f7f3b62c4e479fb2b13f24.poster.avif?t=1748595734\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/6b246f27b7f7f3b62c4e479fb2b13f24.webm?t=1748595734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/6b246f27b7f7f3b62c4e479fb2b13f24.mp4?t=1748595734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/26c0807bcbca5c38cd7d913e7a01f3e4.poster.avif?t=1748595734\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/26c0807bcbca5c38cd7d913e7a01f3e4.webm?t=1748595734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/26c0807bcbca5c38cd7d913e7a01f3e4.mp4?t=1748595734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the ultimate strategy among over a hundred types of cards! Uncovering unexpected </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >powerful synergies and combos is the key to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/86ec22a7c929771c92ce355c9596761a.avif?t=1748595734\" width=600 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/1913dec48851db4003f49af181a5a7dc.poster.avif?t=1748595734\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/1913dec48851db4003f49af181a5a7dc.webm?t=1748595734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/1913dec48851db4003f49af181a5a7dc.mp4?t=1748595734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The most important thing in this game is intelligence! Health is intelligence, purchases are </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >intelligence! If your intelligence reaches 0, you will die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, mindless play means certain doom! Can you maintain your intelligence until the end?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/9364cf838145739f45bef279239d9266.avif?t=1748595734\" width=600 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/30358d796351ad9b8aab829ef9ab3a63.poster.avif?t=1748595734\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/30358d796351ad9b8aab829ef9ab3a63.webm?t=1748595734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/30358d796351ad9b8aab829ef9ab3a63.mp4?t=1748595734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If the game feels challenging, don't worry! Cirno will provide you with useful tips to help you build a more efficient deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3546240/extras/b87e22933fe39de187005d2f8844f6a7.avif?t=1748595734\" width=600 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share your thoughts and create a more enjoyable and beneficial experience together. It will be an opportunity to share various strategies and tips and grow together!</p>",
